column5: One from today.
Ayyyyyyyy Carrumba!
photoshoped                jk Dave. Thats one big bucketmouth !!!
Nice! How many gallons of sunblock have you gone through?
Haven't used any yet. But I dress like this.
Giant Grouper?
Walloping websnappers!  I need a vacation!
Yup.
That could definetely qualify as a BRUTE Dave.  Nice big fish for sure !!
Goliath grouper???
Oh my! Did you subdue that beast on the "Punisher" Dave?
When was it caught? Why don't you submit it in the tournament and see what happens, maybe they'll mistake it for a bass!
Where are all the tarpon pics?
Nice Dave!  Bring on the pics.  Paul
sick !!
What, you couldn't lift it out for a real pic???   Just remember no vertical hold....
Tarpon fishing blows right now for some reason Bill. We have only seen 12 tarpon on 2 trips. Should be seeing 100 per trip right now. Only one jump off.
Nope. Bottom stick with 80# mono.
Ugh, that sucks man..  Usually as we are leaving in late March, early April the tarpon are turning on!
Just means I have to come back Bill.
Great excuse
